---
/**
 * Sidebar Discreta.
 * Apresentação rápida do autor e links mínimos.
 */
---

<aside class="sidebar" aria-label="Sobre o Taverneiro">
  <div class="sidebar__author">
    <div class="sidebar__avatar" aria-hidden="true">
      <!-- Placeholder para foto/ilustração do Mob -->
      <svg
        width="40"
        height="40"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="1.5"
      >
        <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
        <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="sidebar__bio">
      <h3 class="sidebar__name">Magnus Silvershield</h3>
      <p class="sidebar__role">Taverneiro e Guardião dos Tomos.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="sidebar__quote">
    "Uma caneca quente e uma boa história.<br />
    É tudo que um aventureiro precisa."
  </p>

  <nav class="sidebar__links" aria-label="Links Sociais">
    <a href="/comunidade" class="sidebar__link"
      >Substack</a
    >
    <a href="/comunidade" class="sidebar__link"
      >Instagram</a
    >
    <a href="/comunidade" class="sidebar__link"
      >GitHub</a
    >
  </nav>
</aside>

<style>
  .sidebar {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background-color: var(--surface-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    height: fit-content;
    position: sticky;
    top: var(--space-24); /* Fica fixo ao rolar a página */
  }

  .sidebar__author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .sidebar__avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background-color: var(--color-deep-space);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-starlight-gold);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .sidebar__name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-ivory);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
  }

  .sidebar__role {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-ivory-subtle);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .sidebar__quote {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-ivory-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .sidebar__links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .sidebar__link {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-ivory-subtle);
    transition:
      color var(--transition-fast),
      text-shadow var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .sidebar__link:hover {
    color: var(--color-starlight-gold);
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(212, 176, 106, 0.3);
  }
</style>
